\id PHM - Fore NT [for] -Papua New Guinea 1974 (web version -2013) 
\h Pirimoni 
\toc1 Pirimoni Ae Isa Poro Kaentiye 
\toc2 Pirimoni 
\toc3 Prm 
\mt1 PIRIMONI AE ISA PORO KAENTIYE  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Naeba Poronawe. Karaisiti Isu, aeka iga'na punataga mintuwe. Naebe, tao'yagara Timotibe, tasigeba ma nkisapa Pirimoni kaeti kaeyuse. Kaeba tasibugai ntagara ka yugare pompene.  
\v 2 Piya, kaewa, tamana Apiyawa, tao'maenti ntagara Akipasiwa, kae namapi monota ai'aru pe kinana, sumagira tigeti kaeyuse.   
\p
\v 3 Tabarempa Koti, Wa'ega Isu Karaisiti, isigetisa awagaenabe tintawama paruyenabe tigeti waiyeno.   
\s1 Pirimoni aogima nkaegarantiye  
\p
\v 4 Naeba kaeka nunamunepisa esugatamagi, Kotinempakati na'mu pugatauwe, omuwe.  
\v 5 Piya, naeba abopa kaeka maya yewe: Kaeba Wa'ega Isuka kamatiti'ena potamagina, Kotiti atokaenta kinapa, agu kao'ena puwaitane. Pika yega, abima Kotika na'mu puwe.  
\v 6 Piya, kaeba wasanage ampa kabo puma kamatiti'ena piya pega, a'ya'waema Karaisititisa aogiyena maeyompentana igeba agaka, nunamu yuwe.  
\v 7 Owe, nao'yagara, Kotiti atokaenta kina agu kao'ena puwaitampe, pintana intawama esegi puwaitaka, nantawama paruyena pegi asugasima na'mu puwe.   
\s1 Kayokaya yagara Onisimasi ae kamanane  
\p
\v 8 Piyama naeba Karaisiti nkawamutaka: Kaeba aogiyena po, esegima ugamosinta kanara yosine.  
\v 9 Pigoya, naeba karena, Karaisiti Isu ae iga'na yagara ibaba mintuwe. Piya, esegi kamanapa kampa ukuboka, agu kao'ena puma paebuma ugamukuwe.  
\v 10 Naeba maya yuwe: Yagarane Onisimasika kabigauwe. Naeba iga'na namapi minta, mono omintone. Pintana aogima abima, pigoyema yagarane kanta puma abora mintemine. Kaeba agama aogi potao.  
\v 11 Piya, aeba paipa kampa aogi yuga puma kao'maentemine. Ibaba aeba kanara aogi yuga puma, kaepe naepe tasiyo'maekiye.   
\p
\v 12 Ibaba naeba agarubaogana, aeba mayama naunkantayaga to kaeti waye.  
\v 13 Piya, naeba aogi mono kamana yuwagini iga'na namapi nataugu mintoka, Onisimasipa mata'i nao'maekenaga araku'ma ababosinta, kae maru mpaema naomaeyamisine.  
\v 14 Pipa naene kampagi uwa araku'magi, kampa esegi pugatauwe. Nae nabemika, kaeka ntapiyenabisa aogi po.   
\p
\v 15 Piya, kasa yagara aboragina agora to ababikibempeka, a'yo kagaite kanantipayawema napiyuwe.  
\v 16 Piya, ibaba uwa kayokaya yagaraba kampaye. Aeba Isu nkaegarami kayokaya yagara mintiye. Pi tabugai tao'yagaraga naepa nabugaikana, kaeba asunagasima tabera potakibenema abuwe. Piya, yoga yagaraga, Wa'ega aegaranta yagara, aepa aogima ababo.   
\p
\v 17 Piya, naeka: Nao'yagara, naege ka yugara piyema napiyempepa, Onisimasi to kakema nababempesa puma ababo.  
\v 18 Pigoya, ka'ena kamparaga pugatama, ireta pugatakanapa, nae nagera atao.  
\v 19 Iretawapa naene ikapukuwe. Tagane. Naeba Poronawe. Ma nkisapa nayantepisa kaeyuwe. We, kaeba nae kamana abima e'wasa maentampe, pika iretaba tabera punatampene. Aerawane. Pikaba kampa yuwe.  
\v 20 We, nao'yagara, Wa'egawama nkageraka ka'mu punatamagina, pi Karaisiti nkagega'eraka aogi potamagina paruyena punatao.   
\p
\v 21 Naeba abopa, pi kamana'ne wasikibene. Piya pega, naeba ma nkisapa kaeti kaeyano. Kamana'ne ugamosa puma, ka'isa napiyenagatasa amato pukibenema, abuntuwe.  
\v 22 Pigoya, Koti nunamuripa abiritaka naeba tigeti kananoma, napiyuwe. Piya, ka maru nae'ena akusanataga kaege ampiyeno.   
\s1 Kamana uma nagarintiye  
\p
\v 23 Pigoya, Epaparasi aeba: Aya pene, ugamiye. Aeba Naebe Karaisiti nkiga'na yagararasawe.  
\v 24 Pigoya, a'ya'ma yuga kina'ne: Makabe, Arisitakasibe, Timasibe, Arukube, igeba pabiyama: Aya pene, yewe.   
\p
\v 25 Pigoya, Wa'ega Isu Karaisiti aetisa awagaena tiguti waiyeno.  
\q1 Poro piya isa kaentiye.   